    body: "<p></p><iframe\n          width=\"560\"\n          height=\"300\"\n          frameBorder=\"0\"\n          allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\"\n          allowFullScreen\n          title=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7RyEp3JKcMY\"\n          src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7RyEp3JKcMY\"\n        ></iframe><p><br>Family coaching background provided the passion that Edwards uses to help Clark County hoopsters.</p><p><a target='_blank' title=\"http://www.clarkcountytoday.com/sports/greg-edwards-cagers-basketball-helps-area-youth-prepare-for-high-school-play/#.W70302hKjZu\" href=\"http://www.clarkcountytoday.com/sports/greg-edwards-cagers-basketball-helps-area-youth-prepare-for-high-school-play/#.W70302hKjZu\"><u><strong>Click here to read the full article.</strong></u></a></p><p></p>",
