  {
    title: "Coaching Clinics",
    slug: "coaching-clinics",
    rank: 8,
    body: "<p>CAGERS BASKETBALL ACADEMY WILL OFFER FALL COACHING CLINICS FOR ANY YOUTH COACHES WANTING TO LEARN MORE ABOUT HOW TO TEACH AND COACH YOUTH BASKETBALL.</p><p>The clinics are a must attend event for Hot Shot coaches and any beginner coach working with kids grades 2-8. The clinic will cover all fundamental aspects of man-to-man defense and offensive play and will demonstrate the drills you can use to teach these skills.</p><p>​The clinics are broken up into two 2-1⁄2 hour sessions, with defensive fundamentals covered in the first session and offensive fundamentals covered in the second session.</p><p></p><p>QUESTIONS?<br><strong>CALL COACH EDWARDS AT: (503) 735-5552</strong></p><p></p>",
